Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.57,0:01:55.29,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}極上の未来を作り出そう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.37,0:02:02.20,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}争鳴の空へと飴色のジェットで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.21,0:02:07.33,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}未熟な夢積み込んだらフルスロットル
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.35,0:02:14.30,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}翔ぼう！想いのままに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.27,0:02:24.27,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Touch and go, Catch the sun!
Comment: 0,0:00:24.88,0:00:24.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,=================OPC=================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.20,0:01:18.25,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Touch and go, Catch the sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.39,0:01:24.75,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}为何我们相会于此？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.76,0:01:28.02,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}单纯的数字是无法证明的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.09,0:01:31.70,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}能让一切历史黯然无色的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.75,0:01:34.13,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}神秘大发现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.25,0:01:37.91,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}恰巧合适的 启示的密码
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.94,0:01:41.08,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}那是宇宙级的交感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.12,0:01:48.93,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}你能听见创造新纪元的胎动吗…？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:50.51,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Burning through the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.57,0:01:55.29,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}创造出至高的未来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.37,0:02:02.20,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}乘上琥珀色的喷气飞机 向着争鸣的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.21,0:02:07.33,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}载满不成熟的梦想全力踩下油门
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.35,0:02:14.30,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}飞翔吧！一如所愿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.27,0:02:24.27,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Touch and go, Catch the sun!
